-- Motorola, Nokia Told to Amend LCD Price-Fixing Lawsuit Against Samsung, LG
-- Edvard Pettersson
-- 2010-06-29T18:59:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/motorola-nokia-told-to-amend-lcd-price-fixing-lawsuit-against-samsung-lg.html

          
          
             Motorola Inc., Nokia Oyj and other
buyers of liquid crystal display panels used in handsets need to
refile a price-fixing lawsuit they had brought against makers of
the screens, including Samsung Electronics Co. and LG Display
Co., a judge said.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Edvard Pettersson in Los Angeles at 
 epettersson@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        